"Maternal Instincts"

Rollins' mother Beth throws her a baby shower
while the SVU reports to a four-star hotel where
a famous violinist was raped by her colleague,
Anton Krasnikov. With no memory of the crime,
Anton claims a hired escort drugged and robbed
him, and evidence leads to the shocking return of
Rollins' fugitive sister Kim. Meanwhile, Sgt.
Mike Dodds arrives for his first day at SVU.
